title: 896 Picnic Time Touchdown
description: The Touchdown PRO cutting board is a 15" x 8.75" x 0.75" board made of eco-friendly bamboo in a football design, with 123 square inches of cutting surface. It can be used as a cutting board or serving tray, or use both sides of the board, one for cutting and the other for serving. The backside of the board is solid dark bamboo.

transcripts: The Touchdown cutting board is made of eco-friendly bamboo and a fun football design. The backside of the board is solid dark bamboo with an impressive 123 square inches of cutting surface. It had be used as a cutting board or serving tray. Or use both sides of the board -- one for cutting and the other for serving.  Use your dual purpose Touchdown at your next football game or tailgate party. Officially licensed NFL team logos are also available.
